      </item>
      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To establish an Office of Health Care Competition within the Department of Health and Human Services to administer the National Practitioner Data Base and to collect and make available to the public more information on medical malpractice insurance under that Data Base.</title>
